Guidelime.registerGuide(
[[
[N37-38 Thousand Needles]
[GA Horde]
[D A guide created by T H A C E N#9446\Based on Joana's Speed Leveling guide https://www.joanasworld.com]
01) Make sure you are repaired/resupplied.
02) Run east towards Ironstone Camp (right next to Shimmering Flats) and turn in "[QT1146 The Swarm Grows]" ([G68,64]), accept the next [QA1147 part].
03) Go to the west side of Mirage Raceway and at the dwarf, turn in "[QT1112 Parts for Kravel]" ([G78,77]). Wait a few seconds, then accept "[QA1114 Delivery to the Gnomes]".
04) Next to you, turn in "[QT1114 Delivery to the Gnomes]" ([G78,77]). And accept "[QA1106 Martek the Exiled]".
05) Back at the dwarf next to you accept "[QA1115 The Rumormonger]" ([G78,77], #3 on map).
06) Go east to the Goblin's side and turn in "[QT1183 Goblin Sponsorship]" ([G80,76]), accept "[QA1186 The Eighteenth Pilot]".
07) Next to you, turn in "[QT1186 The Eighteenth Pilot]" ([G80,76]), accept "[QA1187 Razzeric's Tweaking]".
08) Go SW to The Rustmaul Dig Site and do "[QC1147 The Swarm Grows]": kill the needed Silithid bugs. There is only a few Invaders in the cave ([G66,86]) so go for these guys first. The Searchers are up and around the Dig Site. Within the first few mobs you kill, you should receive an item which starts "[QC1148 Parts of the Swarm]", accept it and start doing it in the same area by kill/looting the Silithid mobs, and the items you need can drop from any of them.
09) Make sure you are at least 2 bars away from level 38. Grind on the bugs until you are.
10) Go north to Ironstone Camp and turn in "[QT1147 The Swarm Grows]" ([G68,64], #2 on map).
11) Hearth to XRs.
12) Go west in the XRs and turn in "[QT1148 Parts of the Swarm]" ([G51,30] in The Barrens), accept the next [QA1184 part]. NOTE: If the Cracked Silithid Carapace remains in your bags, destroy it.
13) Go to the Wind Rider Master ([G51,30]) and fly to Thunder Bluff, Mulgore.
14) Go just east a bit to Naal Mistrunner and purchase 3 Soothing Spices from him, this is for a later quest in Dustwallow Marsh, and remember to not sell this to a vendor.
15) Go to The Hunter Rise and turn in "[QT1136 Frostmaw]" ([G61,81]). Accept "[QA1205 Deadmire]".
GET NEW ABILITIES) You should be level 38 now. Get new spells/abilities for your class. 
16) Go to the Bank ([G47,59]) and put the following item into it: Fizzle Brassbolts' Letter. Also if you have a Moonsteel Broadsword in your bank ([G47,59]), get it out now for an easy future turn-in quest. And remember to not sell it to a vendor.
17) Go up to the Wind Rider Master in the middle of TB ([G47,50]) and fly to Brackenwall Village, Dustwallow Marsh.
[NX 38-38 Dustwallow Marsh]
]], "Thacen")
